        "description": "Batch 9 deep enhancement — Seoul-Seoraksan-Sokcho + Pocheon Sanjeong/Herb/Art Valley pair. Single-POI fixed-itinerary methodology (batches 1-5, 8 style). Both tours are SMALL_GROUP — formula different from batch 7/8 private tours. All substantive stops enhanced with 1,000+ char descriptions weaving verified facts. product profile recalibrated to verified-fact 0-1 float scores. Charter-format dimensions previously null: private_tour_fit set to 0.05 (definitionally not private); customizable_route_fit set to 0.1 (small-group fixed itinerary); flexibility_fit set to 0.3 (small-group bus, fixed pickup/drop). Tour-specific: history_culture_fit Seoraksan 0.5 (Sinheungsa 652 + Gwongeumseong 1253 + Tongildaebul 1997) / Pocheon 0.4 (1925 reservoir + quarry restoration). Seoraksan tour: unesco_fit 0.2 → 0.4 (UNESCO Biosphere Reserve since 1982, Korea's only one); autumn_foliage_fit set to 1.0 (catalog-leading); mountain_fit set to 1.0 (catalog-leading); seasonal_fit 0.95. Pocheon tour: romantic_fit set to 0.85 (catalog-second-strongest after Nami tour 0.95); seasonal_fit 0.85; family_fit 0.8 → 0.85. 6 new POIs added to KB (v1.11 → v1.12): seoraksan_national_park, sokcho_tourist_fishery_market, sokcho_beach, sanjeong_lake, herb_island, pocheon_art_valley. KB POI count: 62 → 68.",
